{"tid":509193,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"（召喚連登養龜撚）我隻龜做咩事（有圖慎入）","createTime":"2017-12-25T04:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T17:09:59.000Z","uid":66889,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ee1e31f9c72b56405d160e01b3ee3539bbfab1d3","tid":509193,"uid":66889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:54:40.000Z","msg":"小弟養龜養咗幾年，但呢一年佢隻腳唔知做乜生咗好似腫瘤咁嘅嘢，本身都冇咩事，佢一樣每日食咁多嘢，但呢2日見佢好似大咗同埋紅咗咁，但佢都同以前一樣，無話唔郁，想問下有冇人知咩嚟？唔理佢會唔會有影響?點解會生？有冇方法可以幫吓佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/124815_79f92e119fa448ba2da71b74e154bde3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F124815_79f92e119fa448ba2da71b74e154bde3.jpeg&h=6871d409&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/124824_e5ad9e05c4aa890a029ba01e1a8f5254.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F124824_e5ad9e05c4aa890a029ba01e1a8f5254.jpeg&h=2ac03d60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2邊腳都有 不過一邊大啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/124911_5e85622e88070d0f2ee7cbff437bc33d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F124911_5e85622e88070d0f2ee7cbff437bc33d.jpeg&h=1ab735e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n養咗成4年，由半隻手掌養到大過隻手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/125009_87bca9f9d1873d65710166f8caaac569.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F125009_87bca9f9d1873d65710166f8caaac569.jpeg&h=43a85e03&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/125014_9b33e636eda074180ac5e0d0c9027527.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F125014_9b33e636eda074180ac5e0d0c9027527.jpeg&h=31b78e3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有隻細龜，同佢一齊住，養咗2年幾咁上下，但完全冇呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/125127_839c47540f4d06d9d4f93f98d8c12943.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F125127_839c47540f4d06d9d4f93f98d8c12943.jpeg&h=069ee048&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2隻龜都係食呢隻糧，餵食嘅時候分開，其餘時間一齊放佢地喺沖涼個企缸到，沖涼佢地會匿埋，洗頭水沖涼液應該唔會掂到佢地"},{"pid":"06e102b36c09f5c2e17cd9b8e79636868d841976","tid":509193,"uid":66889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309c9e00baecc869215bccc311685ca3b6d395b5","tid":509193,"uid":66889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654295f1cfab1f99c2143c3e1f60e925658e8bd8","tid":509193,"uid":66889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:05:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d771b905d4d7d363bd3cfa2ac78688ae5172f7d4","tid":509193,"uid":84772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:07:32.000Z","msg":"留名推post幫樓主"},{"pid":"5aff7fefc7afcb7af08d8a7de5367fd31a75396a","tid":509193,"uid":3500,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:09:00.000Z","msg":"直接幫佢睇獸醫啦仲問"},{"pid":"1ce59de293395a420d9368981395d8604925f536","tid":509193,"uid":61653,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:09:25.000Z","msg":"生多咗個春袋"},{"pid":"e0066ab99f07b36f9667c9083747dabefb29217d","tid":509193,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:09:27.000Z","msg":"點解唔即刻睇獸醫？"},{"pid":"2746bda2d0daa051dfaf2f56c259e815619db4eb","tid":509193,"uid":66889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d771b905d4d7d363bd3cfa2ac78688ae517